203
00:12:36,392 --> 00:12:39,071
The main point now is we must ensure

204
00:12:39,072 --> 00:12:41,351
tomorrow's plan goes perfectly.

205
00:12:41,352 --> 00:12:43,071
You're already exposed.

206
00:12:43,072 --> 00:12:45,311
Do you think Song Zhichu
will let you go?

207
00:12:45,312 --> 00:12:47,311
You absolutely cannot go tomorrow.

208
00:12:47,312 --> 00:12:49,240
I'll arrange for you to leave
as soon as possible.

209
00:12:49,240 --> 00:12:50,432
Leave the Song family to me.

210
00:12:50,512 --> 00:12:51,752
Lin Yun.

211
00:12:52,192 --> 00:12:54,831
I already said at Xianhe Restaurant,

212
00:12:54,832 --> 00:12:57,111
we're just partners.

213
00:12:57,112 --> 00:12:58,400
Now, in your current state,

214
00:12:58,400 --> 00:13:00,720
do you still look like the boss
of the Chengyun Society?

215
00:13:00,720 --> 00:13:02,859
Song Zhichu only knows I'm not Xu Yin,

216
00:13:02,860 --> 00:13:04,724
