217
00:13:04,725 --> 00:13:06,845
I must go tomorrow.

218
00:13:11,992 --> 00:13:14,392
Take some medicine before we go.

219
00:13:15,072 --> 00:13:17,182
Even if we're just partners,

220
00:13:17,392 --> 00:13:19,112
I have a duty to protect you.

221
